{"chapter_number":76,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":98,"revelation_place":"madinah","name_arabic":"الانسان","name_complex":"Al-'Insān","name_simple":"Al-Insan","verses_count":31,"pages":[578,580],"meaning":{"text":"The Man","en":"The Man","id":"Manusia"},"verses":[[[1,5592,"76:1","هَلْ أَتَىٰ عَلَى الْإِنسَانِ حِينٌ مِّنَ الدَّهْرِ لَمْ يَكُن شَيْئًا مَّذْكُورًا",["There surely came over man a period of time when he was a thing not worth mentioning.","Bukankah pernah datang kepada manusia waktu dari masa, yang ketika itu belum merupakan sesuatu yang dapat disebut?"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[2,5593,"76:2","إِنَّا خَلَقْنَا الْإِنسَانَ مِن نُّطْفَةٍ أَمْشَاجٍ نَّبْتَلِيهِ فَجَعَلْنَاهُ سَمِيعًا بَصِيرًا",["Surely We have created man from a small life-germ uniting (itself): We mean to try him, so We have made him hearing, seeing.","Sungguh, Kami telah menciptakan manusia dari setetes mani yang bercampur yang Kami hendak mengujinya (dengan perintah dan larangan), karena itu Kami jadikan dia mendengar dan melihat."],578,29,58,231,null,null],[3,5594,"76:3","إِنَّا هَدَيْنَاهُ السَّبِيلَ إِمَّا شَاكِرًا وَإِمَّا كَفُورًا",["Surely We have shown him the way: he may be thankful or unthankful.","Sungguh, Kami telah menunjukkan kepadanya jalan yang lurus; ada yang bersyukur dan ada pula yang kufur."],578,29,58,231,null,null],[4,5595,"76:4","إِنَّا أَعْتَدْنَا لِلْكَافِرِينَ سَلَاسِلَ وَأَغْلَالًا وَسَعِيرًا",["Surely We have prepared for the unbelievers chains and shackles and a burning fire.","Sungguh, Kami telah menyediakan bagi orang-orang kafir rantai, belenggu dan neraka yang menyala-nyala."],578,29,58,231,null,null],[5,5596,"76:5","إِنَّ الْأَبْرَارَ يَشْرَبُونَ مِن كَأْسٍ كَانَ مِزَاجُهَا كَافُورًا",["Surely the righteous shall drink of a cup the admixture of which is camphor","Sungguh, orang-orang yang berbuat kebajikan akan minum dari gelas (berisi minuman) yang campurannya adalah air kafur,"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[6,5597,"76:6","عَيْنًا يَشْرَبُ بِهَا عِبَادُ اللَّهِ يُفَجِّرُونَهَا تَفْجِيرًا",["A fountain from which the servants of Allah shall drink; they make it to flow a (goodly) flowing forth.","(yaitu) mata air (dalam surga) yang diminum oleh hamba-hamba Allah dan mereka dapat memancarkannya dengan sebaik-baiknya."],579,29,58,231,null,null],[7,5598,"76:7","يُوفُونَ بِالنَّذْرِ وَيَخَافُونَ يَوْمًا كَانَ شَرُّهُ مُسْتَطِيرًا",["They fulfill vows and fear a day the evil of which shall be spreading far and wide.","Mereka memenuhi nazar dan takut akan suatu hari yang azabnya merata di mana-mana."],579,29,58,231,null,null],[8,5599,"76:8","وَيُطْعِمُونَ الطَّعَامَ عَلَىٰ حُبِّهِ مِسْكِينًا وَيَتِيمًا وَأَسِيرًا",["And they give food out of love for Him to the poor and the orphan and the captive:","Dan mereka memberikan makanan yang disukainya kepada orang miskin, anak yatim dan orang yang ditawan,"],579,29,58,231,null,null],[9,5600,"76:9","إِنَّمَا نُطْعِمُكُمْ لِوَجْهِ اللَّهِ لَا نُرِيدُ مِنكُمْ جَزَاءً وَلَا شُكُورًا",["We only feed you for Allah's sake; we desire from you neither reward nor thanks:","(sambil berkata), “Sesungguhnya kami memberi makanan kepadamu hanyalah karena mengharapkan keridhaan Allah, kami tidak mengharap balasan dan terima kasih dari kamu."],579,29,58,231,null,null],[10,5601,"76:10","إِنَّا نَخَافُ مِن رَّبِّنَا يَوْمًا عَبُوسًا قَمْطَرِيرًا",["Surely we fear from our Lord a stern, distressful day.","Sungguh, kami takut akan (azab) Tuhan pada hari (ketika) orang-orang berwajah masam penuh kesulitan.”"],579,29,58,231,null,null],[11,5602,"76:11","فَوَقَاهُمُ اللَّهُ شَرَّ ذَٰلِكَ الْيَوْمِ وَلَقَّاهُمْ نَضْرَةً وَسُرُورًا",["Therefore Allah win guard them from the evil of that day and cause them to meet with ease and happiness;","Maka Allah melindungi mereka dari kesusahan hari itu, dan memberikan kepada mereka keceriaan dan kegembiraan."],579,29,58,231,null,null],[12,5603,"76:12","وَجَزَاهُم بِمَا صَبَرُوا جَنَّةً وَحَرِيرًا",["And reward them, because they were patient, with garden and silk,","Dan Dia memberi balasan kepada mereka karena kesabarannya (berupa) surga dan (pakaian) sutera."],579,29,58,231,null,null],[13,5604,"76:13","مُّتَّكِئِينَ فِيهَا عَلَى الْأَرَائِكِ ۖ لَا يَرَوْنَ فِيهَا شَمْسًا وَلَا زَمْهَرِيرًا",["Reclining therein on raised couches, they shall find therein neither (the severe heat of) the sun nor intense cold.","Di sana mereka duduk bersandar di atas dipan, di sana mereka tidak melihat (merasakan teriknya) matahari dan tidak pula dingin yang berlebihan."],579,29,58,231,null,null],[14,5605,"76:14","وَدَانِيَةً عَلَيْهِمْ ظِلَالُهَا وَذُلِّلَتْ قُطُوفُهَا تَذْلِيلًا",["And close down upon them (shall be) its shadows, and its fruits shall be made near (to them), being easy to reach.","Dan naungan (pepohonan)nya dekat di atas mereka dan dimudahkan semudah-mudahnya untuk memetik (buah)nya."],579,29,58,231,null,null],[15,5606,"76:15","وَيُطَافُ عَلَيْهِم بِآنِيَةٍ مِّن فِضَّةٍ وَأَكْوَابٍ كَانَتْ قَوَارِيرَا",["And there shall be made to go round about them vessels of silver and goblets which are of glass,","Dan kepada mereka diedarkan bejana-bejana dari perak dan piala-piala yang bening laksana kristal,"],579,29,58,231,null,null],[16,5607,"76:16","قَوَارِيرَ مِن فِضَّةٍ قَدَّرُوهَا تَقْدِيرًا",["(Transparent as) glass, made of silver; they have measured them according to a measure.","kristal yang jernih terbuat dari perak, mereka tentukan ukurannya yang sesuai (dengan kehendak mereka)."],579,29,58,231,null,null],[17,5608,"76:17","وَيُسْقَوْنَ فِيهَا كَأْسًا كَانَ مِزَاجُهَا زَنجَبِيلًا",["And they shall be made to drink therein a cup the admixture of which shall be ginger,","Dan di sana mereka diberi segelas minuman bercampur jahe."],579,29,58,231,null,null],[18,5609,"76:18","عَيْنًا فِيهَا تُسَمَّىٰ سَلْسَبِيلًا",["(Of) a fountain therein which is named Salsabil.","(Yang didatangkan dari) sebuah mata air (di surga) yang dinamakan Salsabil"],579,29,58,231,null,null],[19,5610,"76:19","وَيَطُوفُ عَلَيْهِمْ وِلْدَانٌ مُّخَلَّدُونَ إِذَا رَأَيْتَهُمْ حَسِبْتَهُمْ لُؤْلُؤًا مَّنثُورًا",["And round about them shall go youths never altering in age; when you see them you will think them to be scattered pearls.","Dan mereka dikelilingi oleh para pemuda yang tetap muda. Apabila kamu melihatnya, akan kamu kira mereka, mutiara yang bertaburan."],579,29,58,232,null,null],[20,5611,"76:20","وَإِذَا رَأَيْتَ ثَمَّ رَأَيْتَ نَعِيمًا وَمُلْكًا كَبِيرًا",["And when you see there, you shall see blessings and a great kingdom.","Dan apabila engkau melihat (keadaan) di sana (surga), niscaya engkau akan melihat berbagai macam kenikmatan dan kerajaan yang besar."],579,29,58,232,null,null],[21,5612,"76:21","عَالِيَهُمْ ثِيَابُ سُندُسٍ خُضْرٌ وَإِسْتَبْرَقٌ ۖ وَحُلُّوا أَسَاوِرَ مِن فِضَّةٍ وَسَقَاهُمْ رَبُّهُمْ شَرَابًا طَهُورًا",["Upon them shall be garments of fine green silk and thick silk interwoven with gold, and they shall be adorned with bracelets of silver, and their Lord shall make them drink a pure drink.","Mereka berpakaian sutera halus yang hijau dan sutera tebal dan memakai gelang terbuat dari perak, dan Tuhan memberikan kepada mereka minuman yang bersih (dan suci)."],579,29,58,232,null,null],[22,5613,"76:22","إِنَّ هَٰذَا كَانَ لَكُمْ جَزَاءً وَكَانَ سَعْيُكُم مَّشْكُورًا",["Surely this is a reward for you, and your striving shall be recompensed.","Inilah balasan untukmu, dan segala usahamu diterima dan diakui (Allah)."],579,29,58,232,null,null],[23,5614,"76:23","إِنَّا نَحْنُ نَزَّلْنَا عَلَيْكَ الْقُرْآنَ تَنزِيلًا",["Surely We Ourselves have revealed the Quran to you revealing (it) in portions.","Sesungguhnya Kamilah yang menurunkan Al-Qur'an kepadamu (Muhammad) secara berangsur-angsur."],579,29,58,232,null,null],[24,5615,"76:24","فَاصْبِرْ لِحُكْمِ رَبِّكَ وَلَا تُطِعْ مِنْهُمْ آثِمًا أَوْ كَفُورًا",["Therefore wait patiently for the command of your Lord, and obey not from among them a sinner or an ungrateful one.","Maka bersabarlah untuk (melaksanakan) ketetapan Tuhanmu, dan janganlah engkau ikuti orang yang berdosa dan orang yang kafir di antara mereka."],579,29,58,232,null,null],[25,5616,"76:25","وَاذْكُرِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ بُكْرَةً وَأَصِيلًا",["And glorify the name of your Lord morning and evening.","Dan sebutlah nama Tuhanmu pada (waktu) pagi dan petang."],579,29,58,232,null,null],[26,5617,"76:26","وَمِنَ اللَّيْلِ فَاسْجُدْ لَهُ وَسَبِّحْهُ لَيْلًا طَوِيلًا",["And during part of the night adore Him, and give glory to Him (a) long (part of the) night.","Dan pada sebagian dari malam, maka bersujudlah kepada-Nya dan bertasbihlah kepada-Nya pada bagian yang panjang di malam hari."],580,29,58,232,null,null],[27,5618,"76:27","إِنَّ هَٰؤُلَاءِ يُحِبُّونَ الْعَاجِلَةَ وَيَذَرُونَ وَرَاءَهُمْ يَوْمًا ثَقِيلًا",["Surely these love the transitory and neglect a grievous day before them.","Sesungguhnya mereka (orang kafir) itu mencintai kehidupan (dunia) dan meninggalkan hari yang berat (hari akhirat) di belakangnya."],580,29,58,232,null,null],[28,5619,"76:28","نَّحْنُ خَلَقْنَاهُمْ وَشَدَدْنَا أَسْرَهُمْ ۖ وَإِذَا شِئْنَا بَدَّلْنَا أَمْثَالَهُمْ تَبْدِيلًا",["We created them and made firm their make, and when We please We will bring in their place the likes of them by a change.","Kami telah menciptakan mereka dan menguatkan persendian tubuh mereka. Tetapi, jika Kami menghendaki, Kami dapat mengganti dengan yang serupa mereka."],580,29,58,232,null,null],[29,5620,"76:29","إِنَّ هَٰذِهِ تَذْكِرَةٌ ۖ فَمَن شَاءَ اتَّخَذَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّهِ سَبِيلًا",["Surely this is a reminder, so whoever pleases takes to his Lord a way.","Sungguh, (ayat-ayat) ini adalah peringatan, maka barangsiapa menghendaki (kebaikan bagi dirinya) tentu dia mengambil jalan menuju kepada Tuhannya."],580,29,58,232,null,null],[30,5621,"76:30","وَمَا تَشَاءُونَ إِلَّا أَن يَشَاءَ اللَّهُ ۚ إِنَّ اللَّهَ كَانَ عَلِيمًا حَكِيمًا",["And you do not please except that Allah please, surely Allah is Knowing, Wise;","Tetapi kamu tidak mampu (menempuh jalan itu), kecuali apabila Allah kehendaki Allah. Sungguh, Allah Maha Mengetahui, Mahabijaksana."],580,29,58,232,null,null],[31,5622,"76:31","يُدْخِلُ مَن يَشَاءُ فِي رَحْمَتِهِ ۚ وَالظَّالِمِينَ أَعَدَّ لَهُمْ عَذَابًا أَلِيمًا",["He makes whom He pleases to enter into His mercy; and (as for) the unjust, He has prepared for them a painful chastisement.","Dia memasukkan siapa pun yang Dia kehendaki ke dalam rahmat-Nya (surga). Adapun bagi orang-orang zhalim disediakan-Nya azab yang pedih."],580,29,58,232,null,null]],[[[1,11,578,"&#xfbdc;","word","هَلْ",["Has","waktu"]],[2,11,578,"&#xfbdd;","word","أَتَىٰ",["(there) come","dari"]],[3,11,578,"&#xfbde;","word","عَلَى",["upon","masa"]],[4,11,578,"&#xfbdf;","word","الْإِنْسَانِ",["man","tidaklah"]],[5,11,578,"&#xfbe0;","word","حِينٌ",["a period","dia"]],[6,11,578,"&#xfbe1;","word","مِنَ",["of","sesuatu"]],[7,11,578,"&#xfbe2;","word","الدَّهْرِ",["time","yang disebut"]],[8,11,578,"&#xfbe3;","word","لَمْ",["not",""]],[9,11,578,"&#xfbe4;","word","يَكُنْ",["he was",""]],[10,11,578,"&#xfbe5;","word","شَيْئًا",["a thing",""]],[11,11,578,"&#xfbe6;","word","مَذْكُورًا",["mentioned",""]],[12,11,578,"&#xfbe7;","end","ﯧ",[null,null]]],[[1,12,578,"&#xfbe8;","word","إِنَّا",["Indeed, We","sesungguhnya Kami"]],[2,12,578,"&#xfbe9;","word","خَلَقْنَا",["[We] created","Kami telah menciptakan"]],[3,12,578,"&#xfbea;","word","الْإِنْسَانَ",["man","manusia"]],[4,12,578,"&#xfbeb;","word","مِنْ",["from","dari"]],[5,12,578,"&#xfbec;","word","نُطْفَةٍ",["a semen-drop","setetes mani"]],[6,12,578,"&#xfbed;","word","أَمْشَاجٍ",["a mixture","bercampur"]],[7,12,578,"&#xfbee;","word","نَبْتَلِيهِ",["(that) We test him","Kami mengujinya"]],[8,12,578,"&#xfbef;","word","فَجَعَلْنَاهُ",["so We made (for) him","maka Kami jadikan ia"]],[9,12,578,"&#xfbf0;","word","سَمِيعًا",["hearing","mendengar"]],[10,13,578,"&#xfbf1;","word","بَصِيرًا",["and sight","melihat"]],[11,13,578,"&#xfbf2;","end","ﯲ",[null,null]]],[[1,13,578,"&#xfbf3;","word","إِنَّا",["Indeed, We","sesungguhnya Kami"]],[2,13,578,"&#xfbf4;","word","هَدَيْنَاهُ